# Booking Page Cutover Plan: "The Wide Split"

We are migrating the existing multi-step [BookingWizard](file:///Users/bronsonallen/Documents/dev/sponsra/app/%28portal%29/%5Bslug%5D/booking/BookingWizard.tsx#29-255) to the new "Wide Split" layout.

## Goals
1.  **Layout**: "Wide Split" design (Left Content + Right Sticky Sidebar) matching `/test/booking-1`.
2.  **Tech**: React, CSS Modules (one per component), App Design Tokens ([globals.css](file:///Users/bronsonallen/Documents/dev/sponsra/app/styles/globals.css)).
3.  **Functionality**: Preserve all existing logic (availability, locking, Stripe).

